Hi Alexander. Thanks for sharing your code.

Colin

On Mon, 1 Jul 2019 at 22:23, artful.soft@... [neat] <
neat@yahoogroups.com> wrote:

> We would like to announce our NEAT implementation inspired by Ken Stanley
> papers and Colin Green's SharpNEAT project.
>
> The code is neither polished, nor well documented and it is definitely not
> bugs free, but it can solve XOR problem at least (demo
> <https://youtu.be/G-yjV7KaWog>).
>
>
> The library is fully compatible with Unity3D version 2018.3 and above, we
> successfully used it in our Unity pet projects like this
> <https://youtu.be/eY2s_9Fy1fU>one.
>
> Link to source <https://github.com/IrmaVeoll/Neatron> code:
> https://github.com/IrmaVeoll/Neatron.
>
>
>

--000000000000de2e1c058ccd827e
